{{vgname|真侍魂 霸王丸地狱变|ja=真 SAMURAI SPIRITS 覇王丸地獄変|en=Samurai Shodown II|diff=yes}}是一款由[[SNK|SNK]]公司制作和发行的[[格斗类游戏|格斗类游戏]]。游戏首先于1994年在[[街机|街机]]发行，后于SNK的[[NEOGEO|NEOGEO]]发行。<ref name="gamefaqs">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamefaqs.com/neo/519956-samurai-shodown-ii/data| title = Release information| publisher = [[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]| date = | accessdate = 2015-11-05| language = en| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211742/http://www.gamefaqs.com/neo/519956-samurai-shodown-ii/data| dead-url = no}}</ref>

由于受到首作《[[侍魂_(1993年遊戲)|侍魂]]》的好评以及爱好者的热情，SNK制作了续作。本作几乎囊括了前作的人物，并添加了几个新角色。游戏还重新设定了控制和动作。

《真侍魂 霸王丸地狱变》收到了众多好评，甚至超过前作。<ref name="review4">{{cite web |last=Gerstmann |first=Jeff |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/samurai-shodown-2-review/1900-2545690/ |title=Samurai Shodown II Review |publisher=GameSpot.com |date=2013-10-10 |accessdate=2015-04-10 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920014343/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/samurai-shodown-2-review/1900-2545690/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

